&lt;b&gt;Hey LET Folks,&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
We are back again with our latest offer with some latest updates from VMHaus&lt;br&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
&lt;b&gt;January 2018 Updates&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;
- Voted the &lt;b&gt;Best New Provider 2017&lt;/b&gt; (We sincerely thank everyone who supported us &amp; voted for us!)&lt;br&gt;
- Successful launch of our new Los Angeles location with fully redundant core design. Dual core switches and dual Juniper gears.&lt;br&gt;
- Added new payment method - **Alipay**&lt;br&gt;
- The overall London infrastructure maintenance on 21st January was a success although with some minor hiccup. All Hypervisors were successfully updated and patched. Network upgrades completed and it will allow us to properly scale for further growth. Major network changes to further enhance the security of our London infrastructure.&lt;br&gt;
- VMHaus has acquired our own **Cogent(AS174)** port and **LONAP Internet Exchange** ports. Both are currently in provisioning stage and will be up in a week.&lt;br&gt;
- BGP Peering infrastructure for clients in LAX has been successfully setup and tested. **We will reply to all LAX BGP request shortly.**&lt;br&gt;
- Due to high demands, we have also added **CentOS 6.9** template for 512MB plans and above&lt;br&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
The team at VMHaus had a busy January and things have finally settled down. In the next months, we will be shifting our focus to the development of Bonsai. Features such as usage graphs, client-end custom ISO, client-end backup, automated BGP and many more are all coming to Bonsai.&lt;br&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
&lt;b&gt;Offers Section&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;
As always, not everyone likes everyone and everything, it would be a pretty boring world if we did, so we offer a 7-day money back guarantee if the performance isn't as described. (Money back only applies to PayPal, Alipay currently is unable to be refunded)&lt;br&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
&lt;b&gt;Our Features - Instant Activation (Subject to fraud checks)&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;
- Pure NVMe Powered Storage - It's even faster than SATA SSD Disks!&lt;br&gt;
- One-click OS Install - CentOS, Debian, Ubuntu&lt;br&gt;
- Custom ISO - Bring your own ISO. (Just submit a ticket)&lt;br&gt;
- Automated Backup - All VPS are automatically backed up on site.&lt;br&gt;
- Free DDoS Protection&lt;br&gt;
- Hourly billing&lt;br&gt;
- SSH Key Support!&lt;br&gt;
- BGP Sessions (Just open a ticket with your ASN and prefixes)&lt;br&gt;
- Free ASN Registration service (for clients who maintains monthly servers worth $50)&lt;br&gt;
- Low latency to majority of UK Content Providers via our London Internet Exchange Port (LINX LON1 &amp; LON2) and LONAP coming up!&lt;br&gt;
